parameters.name: VR
parameters.description: Column contains ion velocity radial component (RTN coordinates, Sun-spacecraft direction) in units of km/s.

parameters.name: XVR
parameters.description: Column contains 1 sigma error in Vr in units of km/s.

parameters.name: VT
parameters.description: Column contains ion velocity North/South component (RTN coordinates, positive northward) in units of km/s.

parameters.name: XVT
parameters.description: Column contains 1 sigma error in Vt in units of km/s.

parameters.name: VN
parameters.description: Column contains ion velocity azimuthal component (RTN coordinates, positive in the direction of planetary motion) in units of km/s.

parameters.name: XVN
parameters.description: Column contains 1 sigma error in Vn in units of km/s.

parameters.name: DEN1
parameters.description: Column contains ion density 1 in units of ions/cm**3.

parameters.name: XDEN1
parameters.description: Column contains 1 sigma error in density 1 in units of ions/cm**3.

parameters.name: WTH1
parameters.description: Column contains ion thermal speed 1 in units of km/s.

parameters.name: XWTH1
parameters.description: Column contains 1 sigma error in thermal speed 1 in units of km/s.

parameters.name: DEN2
parameters.description: Column contains ion density 2 in units of ions/cm**3.

parameters.name: XDEN2
parameters.description: Column contains 1 sigma error in density 2 in units of ions/cm**3.

parameters.name: WTH2
parameters.description: Column contains ion thermal speed 2 in units of km/s.

parameters.name: XWTH2
parameters.description: Column contains 1 sigma error in thermal speed 2 in units of km/s.

parameters.name: TEMP1
parameters.description: Column contains ion temperature 1 in units of eV.

parameters.name: TEMP2
parameters.description: Column contains ion temperature 2 in units of eV.
